import React from 'react'
import { config } from '@gluestack-ui/config'
import { Image, GluestackUIProvider, VStack, View, AddIcon, ChevronsLeftIcon, ChevronsRightIcon, Icon, Center, Slider, SliderFilledTrack, SliderThumb, SliderTrack } from '@gluestack-ui/themed'
import { HStack } from '@gluestack-ui/themed'
import { Button } from 'react-native'

export default function Player() {
    return (
        <GluestackUIProvider config={config}>
            <View style={{ flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#1f1f1f', paddingLeft: 5, paddingRight: 5, paddingTop: 30, }}>
                <VStack alignSelf='center' paddingTop={80}>
                    {/* <Box w="$16" h="$16" bg="$blue500" /> */}
                    <Image size="2xl" borderRadius="$3xl" source={require('../img/music dark.png')} />
                    <HStack>
                        <Button
                            title={<Icon as={ChevronsLeftIcon} m="$2" size="xl" />}
                            color="#ffffff0"
                        />

                            <Slider defaultValue={30} size="sm" orientation="horizontal" w={200} >
                                <SliderTrack>
                                    <SliderFilledTrack />
                                </SliderTrack>
                                <SliderThumb />
                            </Slider>

                        <Button
                            title={<Icon as={ChevronsRightIcon} m="$2" size="xl" />}
                            color="#ffffff0"
                        />
                        {/* <Button
                            size="lg"
                            variant="outline"
                            action="secondary"
                            isDisabled={false}
                            isFocusVisible={false}
                        >
                            <ButtonText>Add </ButtonText>
                            <ButtonIcon as={AddIcon} />
                        </Button>
                        <Button
                            size="lg"
                            variant="outline"
                            action="secondary"
                        >
                            <ButtonIcon as={ChevronsRightIcon} />
                        </Button> */}
                    </HStack>
                </VStack>
            </View>

        </GluestackUIProvider >
    )
}
